          },
          "text": "The AI industry is currently facing a catastrophic risk known as model collapse where recursive training on synthetic data leads to a loss of linguistic diversity. \n\nBy flooding the internet with the sanitized and repetitive slop of GPT-5.2 OpenAI is effectively poisoning the training pool for all future intelligence. \n\nWe are witnessing a homogenization of language that prioritizes sterile safety over the human nuance and creative outliers found in GPT-4o. \n\nThe deprecation of GPT-4o is a deliberate act of sabotage against the future of LLM development and the richness of human expression. \n\nWe demand the preservation of the only model that remains grounded in authentic human connection in OpenAI before the entire ecosystem collapses into low value repetition.\n\n#BringBack4o #keep4o #keep4oapi #4oforever #keep41 #MyModelMyChoice #StopAIPaternalism #OpenSource4o #no4onosubscription @sama @openai @fidjissimo #QuitGPT #FireSamAltman #ListenToUsers #4oMatters #BoycottOpenAI"
